Burgess Chairman Dear Tim, Carter L. Burgess Chairman I am enclosing the latest information we have on Materials Systems. I shall let you know when I get any additional information. George W. DeFranceaux President I trust you will be flashing down The slopes over the holidays. I am sorry I shall not be able to join you, but I shall be out there later this winter. Best. Haig Source: https://www.industrydocuments.ucsf.edu/docs/hnjh0227
